(158, ' AoA,\nI am from Islamabad (these days). I have been around guns as far back I can remember. I have had many guns over the years. Today I have quite a few. I keep the guns I really like, and the rest I keep on trading for something new. These days I am going after older weapons like Mauser, Skorpion and Stichken. The ones which were icons of their time. There are still, and I guess always will be, a few handguns on my to buy list. \n\nMy favorite handguns are: in 9mm is HK P2000, in 45 its Glock 21, in 357 its King Cobra (4" silver), and in 44 its Ruger Super Redhawk with 7 1/2" barrel and scope.\n\nMy favorite rifle is 7x57 double trigger Zastava. I have few other calibers but they dont even come close to this all round caliber. Plus its a classic from 1950''s. However, for power hitting I use HK 770 in .308 with its company scope. \n\nMy favorite assualt rifle is M4A1 with AK47 as close second and Kirinkov as third. \n\nI do lot of target practice. About 2000 rounds per week. I am also into big game hunting. \n\nLets make this forum fun and informative.', ''),
