(372, ' Thanks guys. The Glocks are made in Austria.\n\nThe Glock 19 is a smaller more compact version of the Glock 17. The major difference are:\n\na). Size\nb). Weight\nc). Standard Magazine Capacity ( 15 vs 17 )\nd). Barrel length ( 4 Inch vs 4.5 )\n\nThe 19 is better suited for concealed carry and the 17 is better suited for the range.', ''),
