(389, ' That''s good. I''m sure you care for it and it will InshAllah last you a long time. Most of the same guns are mistreated by guards etc and are exposed to the elements 24/7. That causes them to rust very quickly. \n\nA home or self defense shotgun is much better with a pistol grip. You need freedom of movement in smaller places inside homes/buildings etc and the ability to fire instantly. Fixed / traditional long stocks takes a longer time to shoot as you first have to put it to your shoulder and then take the shot. Those two extra seconds of putting the gun to your shoulder are the difference between life and death in a self defense situation. \n\nAlso the normal long stock makes the gun longer and less maneuverable. Most of the close combat weapons / self defense weapons that you will see worldwide will be as compact as possible.\n\nGenerally for internal home defense Pistols are the best. If however the threat is from outside the building and you have the higher ground like the roof then a shotgun with the right combination of ammo is deadly even if the assailants are carrying AK-47''s.', ''),
