(427, ' My friends i live in karachi my name is Osama and im a new member and im seriously obssessed with guns.\nAbout the shooting range i was also searching for one and there is one at pns karsaz and they have started civillian memberships. It is a very well equipped shooting range with three different ranges pistol, rifle, and shotgun range. You can get the form for 100rs from 9 to 2pm wokring days friday closed The form has a little of complications all the procedures will be explained by navy officials there but you just have to make sure that your license is not issued on any political parties quota it can create problems. The membership fees is the main concern and the info is as follows:\n\nCivillian:\nA  56000rs  700/month  life time\nB  26000rs  1400/month  life time\nC 17000rs (4000rs refundable)  300/visit One year only\n\nStudent: (for upto 22 years only)\nA 10000rs  250/month\nB 5000rs   500/month\n\nCo-operate membership: \n100000rs for 5 personnel  1000/person/month  life time\n\nGuests can only visit with members which will cost guests of a charge of 225/visit', ''),
