(513, ' I have one, Bought it for 33K here in karachi in may 2008. \n[img]http://www.thefiringline.com/forums/attachment.php?attachmentid=35738&d=1220599757[/img]\n\n[img]http://www.thefiringline.com/forums/attachment.php?attachmentid=35739&stc=1&d=1220600732[/img]\n\nI took it for test on Karsaz Range, Couldn''t hit any skeet though, but did damage a couple of cartons. IT shoots gr8, SG rounds(00 buckshot) patterned to about 10-12 inch @ 20 -25 yards. \n\nIt kicks a lot though. Although the folding stock is nice & handy, I would like to get a standard shoulder stock for it. I tried the market here but didnt find any "spare". Can any one tell me where I can get the said thing? I am also looking for its choke tubes, but I believe dealers here lack when it comes to accessories pretty badly.', ''),
