(677, ' [quote=Abbas]The online store thing sounds like a good idea. I''ll start working on it when we cross 100 forum users InshAllah.[/quote]\n\nOne thing I have noticed that arms dealer don’t have cleaning kits rest you can get bullets, guns I went through a couple of good web sites the best and oldest one was Hoppes. They have some good stuff. I was thinking that Cap1 suggested online store and Abbas bhai said after 100 members have joined the forum by this speed we will be there by next month. Why not import some cleaning kits and put them on our online store and maybe somthing else. Members any Idea''s? I hope that’s legal.  Which brand or which kit to go for we can always open a new topic and have a discussion on it.', ''),
