(738, ' [quote]I think QSZ92 is the chinese millitary version capable of firing DAP rounds, CF98 is the same gun in civilian version. NP42 is only has a better barrel life than the CF98. These are my two cents about the gun, if anyone knows better please educate me.[/quote]\nI also have the same info\n\nThe NP42 is my first gun so I can''t really comment on the trigger in DA mode. I''ve only shot a few rounds and I thought it was easier to control than I thought it would be. Trying to get range access if I ever complete the never-ending formalities. It was easier to get the gun than to get range membership. No wonder so many people resort to aerial firing to test their guns. There really should be more training schools and ranges so people can learn and practice properly.', ''),
