(1213, ' Wsalms & Welcome Tareen.\n\n@Acciprone I asked a couple of months back as I wanted some shotguns for Karachi. They won''t send anything to another city and at the most will refer a reliable dealer who carries whatever you require in your city. In the end I ended up buying my guns from Lahore and taking them to Karachi myself by air. Some NWFP dealers do deliver in Punjab if there is a history of good dealing with them but still is a little shady.\n\nAs another example, once I was in Islamabad and after a night out shooting ran out of ammo, as I didn''t deal with any ISB dealers I called mine back home and asked him to call someone in Isb. He did and gave a strong recommendation but the Isb one still charged me Isb rates no matter what I told him, if I said the 9mm''s were Rs. 30 in Lahore and he was selling for Rs. 40, he''s like buy em from Lahore then.. lol.. :lol: \n\nIf there is a large difference in prices of a weapon, you can visit us here in Lahore and come pick up your piece.', ''),
